
/*

Using:

index = (index + 1) & (BUFFER_SIZE - 1);

instead of:

index = (index + 1) % BUFFER_SIZE;

Reason:
Bitwise AND operation is faster than modulo operation on many MCUs
because it avoids division instructions.

This optimization works only when BUFFER_SIZE is a power of 2
(8, 16, 32, 64, etc.).

*/